    "data": [
        [
            [
                ""
            ],
            [
                "As Fabián is walking away, I notice a patch on [his] backpack."
            ],
            [
                "It says “Aukademi’s D&D club”"
            ],
            [
                "Ain’t no way… this dude goes to my same uni?"
            ],
            [
                "That’s why [his] name sounded so familiar."
            ],
            [
                "The universe really likes to do some crazy coincidences."
            ],
            [
                "I stretch and scratch my head."
            ],
            [
                "The event had already taken quite some time, and my back already felt sore from sitting and meeting so many people. "
            ],
            [
                "The worst thing? I still want to go to the bathroom."
            ],
            [
                "I decide to look around, scanning the other tables with many people enjoying their conversations."
            ],
            [
                "As I am looking away, a really nice voice speaks to me. "
            ],
            [
                "Hi, can I sit here?"
            ],
            [
                "I then look at the person in front of me and oh my. "
            ],
            [
                "I’m not usually one that lets someone's body be the first thing they like,"
            ],
            [
                "but it was hard not to focus on the perfect one right in front of me."
            ],
            [
                "Y-yeah… Um… hi."
            ],
            [
                "I feel blood rush right to my cheeks as I try to make a coherent phrase."
            ],
            [
                "I surely look pathetic right now."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, My name is [Gian Carlo]."
            ],
            [
                "And I must say… It’s quite a pleasure meeting you."
            ],
            [
                "I’m [tn]. Nice to meet you too!"
            ],
            [
                "Please, tell me about yourself."
            ],
            [
                "Heh, alright pumpkin."
            ],
            [
                "Since you want to get to know me, I have to tell you that I’m quite a romantic person."
            ],
            [
                "Rom-coms are my favorite movies and well, I really, REALLY like pumpkin pie."
            ],
            [
                "Figures why [he] called me that pet name"
            ],
            [
                "Cool! I watch Rom-coms sometimes"
            ],
            [
                "And what about your hobbies? Do you have any?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah! I’m very social, so I enjoy exploring new places to eat."
            ],
            [
                "I guess that makes me a foodie? Haha!"
            ],
            [
                "Oh, and also, I really enjoy working out and making friends at the gym."
            ],
            [
                "The other day I went to a pilates class and it was so fun! You should come some day."
            ],
            [
                "[He] was very chatty for sure."
            ],
            [
                "It felt refreshing to have someone who I could talk to for hours."
            ],
            [
                "Still, that gym comment made me cringe a little bit."
            ],
            [
                "It made me recall that gym girl from earlier."
            ],
            [
                "I look down at my stomach, and wonder if I was really that pudgy."
            ],
            [
                "B-but you don’t have to come if you don’t want to."
            ],
            [
                "I mean… you already look stunning! We could go anywhere else that you’d like!"
            ],
            [
                "It seems [he] picked up on how I felt."
            ],
            [
                "It Is kind of cute seeing [him] try to make me feel better."
            ],
            [
                "Haha thanks! That’s kinda sweet"
            ],
            [
                "[Gian Carlo] suddenly seemed more bashful compared to"
            ],
            [
                "[his] confident demeanor from earlier and looked away."
            ],
            [
                "Hey [tn], I don’t want to come very straight forward, but…"
            ],
            [
                "you’ve really catched my interest."
            ],
            [
                "I know It’s kinda soon but, I would really appreciate it if you considered going out with me."
            ],
            [
                "I promise I’ll treat you as you deserve-"
            ],
            [
                "Once more, that stupid bell rings"
            ],
            [
                "It almost feels like it knows damn well when to interrupt a good time."
            ],
            [
                "[Gian Carlo] stops in [his] tracks and jolts at the sudden ring."
            ],
            [
                "[He] then quickly grabs a piece of paper and writes something on it."
            ],
            [
                "Here… this is my number."
            ],
            [
                "I’ll wait for your text, or call, or"
            ],
            [
                "you get it pumpkin."
            ],
            [
                "[Giancarlo] then winks at me and smiles with [his] pearly whites."
            ],
            [
                "There’s definitely something that makes me gravitate towards [him]."
            ]
        ],
